Invocation Name: redwood city
Developer Terms of Use
des: Find kids events taking place in Redwood City, California libraries. This skill is intended to connect Redwood City residents to city services and events. Currently, it provides information about kids events taking place in Redwood City libraries. Parents can simply ask their Amazon Alexa enabled devices - Ask Redwood City about kids events - and it will broadcast the events taking place that day. Eventually, many other use cases will be embedded.
